de_greene - Bomb Defusal
by: Dark Nova Studios (DNvCross and DNvLasrever) & Ted "cashed" McIlwain
http://www.dark-nova.net
http://www.tedmcilwain.com

Terrorists:
Joey Greene is holed up in his WWII bunker, and we want him dead.
Blow up the bunker itself or destroy a gas main running to the
bunker to ensure his demise.

Counter-Terrorists:
We must protect Joey Greene! Prevent the terrorists from
blowing up the Greene's bunker and any gas mains that lead
to it.
